reviews.text:
The restuarant might be small yet, It was absolutely amazing!  I was suprised how they made such good broth without any artificial flavouring / msg just for the soup base of the noodles! The kids also loved it for it's sweet chicken wings, lettuce and rice noodles, great for kids! You can choose 3 dofferent kinds of foods to accompany the noodles and choose your soup broth for less than 4£ along with other snacks.
If you are a tourist coming to Hong Kong with your kids, you should definitely try coming here!
Taste is good but a bit overpriced against the nearby restaurant.
